Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.80,0:02:01.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以說如果要用一天來表現人的一生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.07,0:02:01.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(630,0)\an1\pos(96,573)\fs40}第一話\N之後究竟要嘶喊多久才好
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.17,0:02:07.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們現在所處的中學時代正是太陽升起後不久…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.71,0:02:06.76,Default2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好長
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.54,0:02:13.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好短
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.52,0:02:20.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花開
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.79,0:02:29.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,花謝
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.96,0:02:36.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.35,0:02:38.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.78,0:02:39.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.67,0:02:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.40,0:02:47.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.20,0:02:51.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不 沒什麼 沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.89,0:02:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 真漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.62,0:02:58.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己做的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.38,0:03:00.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這麼漂亮的東西自己能做出來嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.51,0:03:02.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很簡單啊 編織出來的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.64,0:03:04.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是編織成鎖鏈狀而已
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.53,0:03:05.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,編織成鎖鏈狀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.50,0:03:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.90,0:03:15.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,白色
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.84,0:03:20.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各種顏色的…女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.82,0:03:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊 真綯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.46,0:03:23.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啊好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.27,0:03:26.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說 由宇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.97,0:03:29.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳覺得玩小鳥是怎麼個玩法？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.84,0:03:30.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩小鳥？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.93,0:03:31.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.61,0:03:34.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在小鳥腿上偷偷繫上一條細鎖鏈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.41,0:03:36.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然後就看它撲棱撲棱像氣球一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.75,0:03:38.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好殘酷！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.24,0:03:40.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想跟妳說話啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.11,0:03:43.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 不要生氣啦 真綯同學
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.88,0:03:46.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學才不是那樣的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.85,0:03:48.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不過她會編鎖鏈！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.67,0:03:49.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.61,0:03:51.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 她很適合紅色！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.56,0:03:53.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為啊 她好白的！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.63,0:03:55.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜託妳說日語
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.75,0:03:56.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吧 就是那啥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.93,0:04:00.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳想和那個叫小鳥遊的女生成為朋友對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.90,0:04:03.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭啦 才不是那樣…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.15,0:04:04.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 其實就是那麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.95,0:04:06.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙在搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.74,0:04:10.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.86,0:04:20.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,報告呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遇到了一個很有趣的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.29,0:04:26.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,表情一會兒一個樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.91,0:04:27.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.62,0:04:28.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.61,0:04:29.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為不行啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.49,0:04:35.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.81,0:04:37.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽叫妳去洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.59,0:04:41.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又在看那個了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.26,0:04:43.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,媽媽叫妳洗澡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:44.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.61,0:04:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,從小我就一直很憧憬
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能夠帶我去往七彩世界的小鳥
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.34,0:04:55.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,藍色
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.10,0:04:57.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,橘色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.30,0:05:02.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑色
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.62,0:05:37.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小…小鳥遊…同學！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.81,0:05:39.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鷹無
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.82,0:05:40.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:43.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,寫作小鳥遊讀作鷹無
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.37,0:05:45.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼這名字會讀成鷹無啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:48.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為有小鳥玩耍的地方是不會有老鷹的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.42,0:05:52.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喔 好聰明的名字！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.83,0:05:59.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個 小鳥遊同學打算加入什麼社團？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.68,0:06:00.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經決定了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.92,0:06:02.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.93,0:06:06.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還沒決定
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.81,0:06:07.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.15,0:06:08.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去一下洗手間
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.09,0:06:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.70,0:06:16.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我平時也是不願意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.49,0:06:18.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想那樣去巴結人的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.96,0:06:21.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳跟我解釋個什麼勁啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.53,0:06:25.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朝霞談話室？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.39,0:06:26.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正是～
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.25,0:06:29.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來喝一杯？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.04,0:06:33.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要再多加些砂糖嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.99,0:06:36.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 好的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.86,0:06:38.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請問 這裡是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.49,0:06:40.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老師沒告訴妳？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.66,0:06:43.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有煩惱的話可以來這裡訴苦喔
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:45.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個人就是諮詢師
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.60,0:06:46.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煩惱？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.43,0:06:52.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊 一旦成為中學生後會突然產生很多煩惱啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.86,0:06:54.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 沒什麼實感
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.88,0:06:55.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.42,0:06:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 砂糖
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.82,0:06:58.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.07,0:07:03.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有煩惱可是件大好事喔 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.47,0:07:07.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果有什麼事想要談心的話就再過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.30,0:07:10.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,光來喝咖啡也行喔
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.24,0:07:11.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.47,0:07:15.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點 繼續加快速度
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.21,0:07:16.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大腿抬高
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.75,0:07:20.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才體驗入部就突然搞什麼衝刺跑
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.35,0:07:22.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這就是中學的品質嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.55,0:07:25.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好 接下來是繞東海道一週
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.89,0:07:27.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,衝出去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.52,0:07:28.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.60,0:07:32.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這樣 速寫各畫兩張
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.73,0:07:34.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,首先兩人組成一組
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.38,0:07:37.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一人擔當模特另一個人畫 然後交換
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.89,0:07:38.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:41.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真難受
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.97,0:07:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳太拼命了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.05,0:07:45.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還是吐一次比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.03,0:07:47.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡吐啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.58,0:07:48.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.44,0:07:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,多謝
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.40,0:07:52.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 申請成為經理的人接下來還要開說明會…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.56,0:07:58.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 晚飯來點清淡的東西就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.61,0:07:59.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咖喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.70,0:08:01.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要 咖喱的話我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.35,0:08:04.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？啊 抱歉 嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.82,0:08:06.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 咖喱 拜託了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.95,0:08:07.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我掛了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.55,0:08:11.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.95,0:08:13.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是七彩小鳥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.93,0:08:14.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.55,0:08:16.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.64,0:08:19.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗚哇 是小鳥的待機畫面
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.86,0:08:21.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個在哪裡有啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.70,0:08:23.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是我自己畫的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.51,0:08:25.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騙人 好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.03,0:08:27.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是也對呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:29.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畫本裡確實沒這張畫
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.57,0:08:32.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難道說妳買的不是初版？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.77,0:08:34.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,初版有這張畫嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:37.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 封面不一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.56,0:08:38.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.68,0:08:39.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好想看一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.52,0:08:45.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.80,0:08:49.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我家裡有啦 初版
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.23,0:08:57.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哇 好大
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.00,0:09:00.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好厲害啊 感覺都能打籃球了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.39,0:09:05.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.20,0:09:08.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.44,0:09:10.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.19,0:09:23.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然好漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.98,0:09:25.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要是妳不嫌棄的話 就送給妳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:26.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:29.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我再做一條就可以了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.65,0:09:30.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.73,0:09:39.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,客人？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.29,0:09:44.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉 小篝她…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.87,0:09:45.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.40,0:09:46.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.24,0:09:46.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不能進來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:48.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等一下！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.56,0:09:55.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.80,0:09:56.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.43,0:09:57.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.12,0:10:00.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這腿啊 是黃泉害得
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.91,0:10:03.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是黃泉害得喔
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.91,0:10:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃吧 法式小圓餅
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.66,0:10:15.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.43,0:10:16.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃咖啡色的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.10,0:10:18.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.74,0:10:22.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.56,0:10:23.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,泥水色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.40,0:10:27.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.00,0:10:29.12,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,亂七八糟的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.03,0:10:36.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,粉紅色的給黃泉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.87,0:10:39.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝是紅色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.47,0:10:43.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總之就是髒兮兮的顏色
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.44,0:10:51.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學 那個…不用勉強自己
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.96,0:10:54.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 我吃
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.33,0:11:03.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好精緻
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.58,0:11:07.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕之類的 上面還有奶油圈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.15,0:11:09.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給 這個給妳
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.94,0:11:14.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好…好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.00,0:11:26.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 梅麗 這個人到底打算待到什麼時候去啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.96,0:11:30.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還不回去嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.59,0:11:35.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回去 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:36.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,篝
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:40.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是篝說的喔 是梅麗在這樣說喔
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.78,0:11:45.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回去 回去
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.99,0:11:50.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去 回去 回…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:54.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 多謝款待
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.20,0:11:57.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再見…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.09,0:12:14.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.55,0:12:16.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.53,0:12:19.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那孩子 好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.42,0:12:32.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真綯 不吃咖喱？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.49,0:12:33.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.09,0:12:37.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.01,0:12:47.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼會流露出那種表情
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.30,0:12:50.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼要給我法式小圓餅
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.99,0:12:52.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.35,0:12:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…是不是做了什麼壞事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.78,0:13:04.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H98827B&\bord0\fr-7\pos(486,401)}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.34,0:13:06.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小鳥遊同學
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.60,0:13:33.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明明說了不行的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.81,0:13:37.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃泉妳可是篝的東西喔
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.15,0:13:39.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要好好負起責任來
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.95,0:13:42.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.86,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.03,0:13:48.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.69,0:15:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}回去×N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.75,0:16:20.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6\fs42}回去×N
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.64,0:16:22.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.10,0:16:38.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呐 黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.18,0:16:40.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳知道車站前的神社在舉辦祭典嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.88,0:16:45.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,班上幾個女生在商量要不要一起去
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.86,0:16:46.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳去不去？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.91,0:16:49.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.55,0:16:55.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我就算了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.69,0:16:57.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎 去嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.89,0:17:00.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有什麼事嗎 我覺得應該很有趣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.81,0:17:01.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:02.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.16,0:17:05.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…怎麼說呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.39,0:17:10.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一旦兩個人單獨相處就不知道該怎麼說話了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.88,0:17:13.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乾脆去告白不就好了 小幡同學
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.13,0:17:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪有這麼簡單啊 真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.44,0:17:21.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然要是我跟老師一樣胸部也那麼大的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.41,0:17:24.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小幡…前輩？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.37,0:17:25.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？！一年生？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.31,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我差不多該走了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.30,0:17:30.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要替我保密啊 小沙耶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.72,0:17:32.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,保密
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.07,0:17:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,呀 這麼快就有煩惱了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.90,0:17:46.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎 擔心自己是不是被討厭了？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:51.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…是黑衣同學對吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:58.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我第一次見到妳的時候就在想了
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.04,0:18:02.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,覺得妳的眼睛十分純淨
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.25,0:18:05.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大概啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.69,0:18:07.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是雙不怎麼會討厭別人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:10.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不怎麼會惹人討厭的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.04,0:18:12.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.92,0:18:15.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不樹敵是件好事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.30,0:18:21.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是啊 在無意中樹敵也是很正常的事
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.40,0:18:22.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很正常的事？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.01,0:18:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯 無論是誰都一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.98,0:18:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要接受這份理所當然就好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胸口很痛吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.76,0:18:37.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是胸口啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.93,0:18:40.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕像被刺傷了一樣疼痛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.51,0:18:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也不會噴血或者產生傷口進而化膿
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.78,0:18:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,總會有人啊 替妳承受這份痛楚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.13,0:18:54.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.80,0:18:57.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 所以說沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.19,0:19:01.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論多痛 受多少傷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.37,0:19:04.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真正受到傷害的都不是妳
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:05.25,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰かのようになりたくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.21,0:19:05.25,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}想要變得和某人一樣堅強
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:09.17,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけどなれるはずもなくて
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.47,0:19:09.17,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}卻又明白無法實現這個目標
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.28,0:19:09.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以要不要再多加些砂糖？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:14.33,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いじけるなら
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.14,0:19:14.33,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}如果為此垂頭喪氣的話
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.45,0:19:16.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人會替我承擔痛苦
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:21.19,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}心の中にいるもう一人の自分が
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.86,0:19:21.19,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}存在於心中的另一個自己
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:19.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有人到底是指誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.58,0:19:21.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又打算留下來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:26.63,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}教えてくれる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.72,0:19:26.63,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}會告訴我答案
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.16,0:19:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.17,0:19:24.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別太晚了喔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.81,0:19:25.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:34.92,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}あるがままなんかじゃきっといられないから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.84,0:19:34.92,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}一成不變畏縮不前的話一定會被淘汰
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:32.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加入…美術部了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:41.74,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}誰もがみんな悩んでもがいてる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.54,0:19:41.74,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論是誰 大家都背負著苦惱而活
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.82,0:19:37.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然畫得好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.66,0:19:38.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妳明白的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.16,0:19:42.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就算想要和我成為朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:48.50,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}弱音吐いたり 愚痴言ってみたり
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.21,0:19:48.50,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}偶爾示弱 偶爾牢騷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.08,0:19:44.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.08,0:19:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.41,0:19:46.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.71,0:19:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.59,0:19:48.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.88,0:19:52.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典…不行！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:55.70,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}そうやって毎日を過ごしてる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.91,0:19:55.70,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}就像這樣度過了每一天
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.98,0:19:56.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了不可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:20:02.55,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}傷つけられることに慣れた僕らは知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.27,0:20:02.55,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}終於習慣受傷的我們已然知曉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.65,0:20:00.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣下去只會傷害黑衣同學而已
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.08,0:20:01.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會傷害我的！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,無論有多痛
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:09.28,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}優しさとか思いだけじゃ生きて行けないことを
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.99,0:20:09.28,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}只靠溫柔的願望無法生存下去
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.00,0:20:07.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…真的真的不會受傷的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.33,0:20:09.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑衣同學
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:15.61,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}だけど自分らしくありたいと思うんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.49,0:20:15.61,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}但是希望可以保持自我的本色
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.79,0:20:11.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以去吧 去玩吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.39,0:20:16.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一起去看各式各樣的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:23.72,IN_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}いつだって 僕ら歩いてく
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.80,0:20:23.72,IN_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)}無論何時 我們都會一路前行
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.67,0:20:22.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各式各樣的…色彩…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.38,0:20:31.34,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,各式各樣的…世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.99,0:21:11.02,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大海所映出的是　天空的蔚藍
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.02,0:21:16.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,繪之空的蔚藍是　天空的大海
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.83,0:21:27.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,淚水中的蔚藍裡　小鳥在飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:45.36,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}あとどれだけ叫べばいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.98,0:21:45.36,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}之後究竟要嘶喊多久才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:51.20,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}あとどれだけ泣けばいいのだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.77,0:21:51.20,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}之後究竟要哭泣多久才好
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:57.51,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}もうやめて わたしはもう走れない
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.63,0:21:57.51,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}快停下吧 我已經無法再奔跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:02.75,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}いつか夢見た世界が閉じる
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.66,0:22:02.75,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}不知何時夢中的世界早已關閉
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:13.42,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}真っ暗で明かりもない 崩れかけたこの道で
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.88,0:22:13.42,ED_chi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}一片漆黑不見光明 在這條瀕臨崩塌的道路上
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.40,0:22:24.91,ED_jap,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\be2}あるはずもないあの時の希望が見えた気がした
